playData.text_entry: Find we a time for frighted peace to pant,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: And breathe short-winded accents of new broils
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: To be commenced in strands afar remote.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: No more the thirsty entrance of this soil
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Shall daub her lips with her own children's blood;
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Nor more shall trenching war channel her fields,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Nor bruise her flowerets with the armed hoofs
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Of hostile paces: those opposed eyes,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Which, like the meteors of a troubled heaven,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: All of one nature, of one substance bred,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Did lately meet in the intestine shock
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: And furious close of civil butchery
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Shall now, in mutual well-beseeming ranks,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: March all one way and be no more opposed
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Against acquaintance, kindred and allies:
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: The edge of war, like an ill-sheathed knife,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: As far as to the sepulchre of Christ,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Whose soldier now, under whose blessed cross
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Forthwith a power of English shall we levy;
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Whose arms were moulded in their mothers' womb
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: To chase these pagans in those holy fields
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Which fourteen hundred years ago were nail'd
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: For our advantage on the bitter cross.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: But this our purpose now is twelve month old,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Therefore we meet not now. Then let me hear
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Of you, my gentle cousin Westmoreland,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: What yesternight our council did decree
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: In forwarding this dear expedience.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: My liege, this haste was hot in question,
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: And many limits of the charge set down
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: A post from Wales loaden with heavy news;
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: A thousand of his people butchered;
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Such beastly shameless transformation,
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: By those Welshwomen done as may not be
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Brake off our business for the Holy Land.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: This match'd with other did, my gracious lord;
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: For more uneven and unwelcome news
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Came from the north and thus it did import:
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: On Holy-rood day, the gallant Hotspur there,
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Young Harry Percy and brave Archibald,
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: That ever-valiant and approved Scot,
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Where they did spend a sad and bloody hour,
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: As by discharge of their artillery,
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: And shape of likelihood, the news was told;
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: For he that brought them, in the very heat
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: And pride of their contention did take horse,
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Uncertain of the issue any way.
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Here is a dear, a true industrious friend,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Sir Walter Blunt, new lighted from his horse.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Stain'd with the variation of each soil
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Betwixt that Holmedon and this seat of ours;
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: And he hath brought us smooth and welcome news.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: The Earl of Douglas is discomfited:
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Ten thousand bold Scots, two and twenty knights,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Balk'd in their own blood did Sir Walter see
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: On Holmedon's plains. Of prisoners, Hotspur took
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Mordake the Earl of Fife, and eldest son
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: To beaten Douglas; and the Earl of Athol,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Of Murray, Angus, and Menteith:
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: And is not this an honourable spoil?
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: A gallant prize? ha, cousin, is it not?
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: In faith,
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: It is a conquest for a prince to boast of.
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Yea, there thou makest me sad and makest me sin
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: In envy that my Lord Northumberland
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Should be the father to so blest a son,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: A son who is the theme of honour's tongue;
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Amongst a grove, the very straightest plant;
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Who is sweet Fortune's minion and her pride:
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Whilst I, by looking on the praise of him,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: See riot and dishonour stain the brow
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Of my young Harry. O that it could be proved
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: That some night-tripping fairy had exchanged
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: In cradle-clothes our children where they lay,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: And call'd mine Percy, his Plantagenet!
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Then would I have his Harry, and he mine.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: But let him from my thoughts. What think you, coz,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Of this young Percy's pride? the prisoners,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Which he in this adventure hath surprised,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: To his own use he keeps; and sends me word,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: I shall have none but Mordake Earl of Fife.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: This is his uncle's teaching; this is Worcester,
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Malevolent to you in all aspects;
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Which makes him prune himself, and bristle up
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: The crest of youth against your dignity.
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: But I have sent for him to answer this;
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: And for this cause awhile we must neglect
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Our holy purpose to Jerusalem.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Cousin, on Wednesday next our council we
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Will hold at Windsor; so inform the lords:
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: But come yourself with speed to us again;
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: For more is to be said and to be done
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Than out of anger can be uttered.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: I will, my liege.
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: SCENE II. London. An apartment of the Prince's.
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Enter the PRINCE OF WALES and FALSTAFF
playData.speaker: WESTMORELAND

playData.text_entry: Now, Hal, what time of day is it, lad?
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Thou art so fat-witted, with drinking of old sack
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: and unbuttoning thee after supper and sleeping upon
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: benches after noon, that thou hast forgotten to
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: demand that truly which thou wouldst truly know.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: What a devil hast thou to do with the time of the
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: day? Unless hours were cups of sack and minutes
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: capons and clocks the tongues of bawds and dials the
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: signs of leaping-houses and the blessed sun himself
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: a fair hot wench in flame-coloured taffeta, I see no
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: reason why thou shouldst be so superfluous to demand
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: the time of the day.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Indeed, you come near me now, Hal; for we that take
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: purses go by the moon and the seven stars, and not
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: by Phoebus, he,'that wandering knight so fair.' And,
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: I prithee, sweet wag, when thou art king, as, God
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: save thy grace,--majesty I should say, for grace
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: thou wilt have none,--
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: No, by my troth, not so much as will serve to
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: prologue to an egg and butter.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Well, how then? come, roundly, roundly.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Marry, then, sweet wag, when thou art king, let not
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: us that are squires of the night's body be called
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: thieves of the day's beauty: let us be Diana's
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: foresters, gentlemen of the shade, minions of the
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: moon; and let men say we be men of good government,
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: being governed, as the sea is, by our noble and
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: chaste mistress the moon, under whose countenance we steal.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Thou sayest well, and it holds well too; for the
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: fortune of us that are the moon's men doth ebb and
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: flow like the sea, being governed, as the sea is,
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: by the moon. As, for proof, now: a purse of gold
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: most resolutely snatched on Monday night and most
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: dissolutely spent on Tuesday morning; got with
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: swearing 'Lay by' and spent with crying 'Bring in;'
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: now in as low an ebb as the foot of the ladder
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: and by and by in as high a flow as the ridge of the gallows.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: By the Lord, thou sayest true, lad. And is not my
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: hostess of the tavern a most sweet wench?
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: As the honey of Hybla, my old lad of the castle. And
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: is not a buff jerkin a most sweet robe of durance?
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: How now, how now, mad wag! what, in thy quips and
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: thy quiddities? what a plague have I to do with a
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Why, what a pox have I to do with my hostess of the tavern?
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Well, thou hast called her to a reckoning many a
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: time and oft.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Did I ever call for thee to pay thy part?
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: No; I'll give thee thy due, thou hast paid all there.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Yea, and elsewhere, so far as my coin would stretch;
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: and where it would not, I have used my credit.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Yea, and so used it that were it not here apparent
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: that thou art heir apparent--But, I prithee, sweet
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: wag, shall there be gallows standing in England when
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: thou art king? and resolution thus fobbed as it is
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: with the rusty curb of old father antic the law? Do
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: not thou, when thou art king, hang a thief.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: No; thou shalt.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Shall I? O rare! By the Lord, I'll be a brave judge.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Thou judgest false already: I mean, thou shalt have
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: the hanging of the thieves and so become a rare hangman.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Well, Hal, well; and in some sort it jumps with my
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: humour as well as waiting in the court, I can tell
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: For obtaining of suits?
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Yea, for obtaining of suits, whereof the hangman
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: hath no lean wardrobe. 'Sblood, I am as melancholy
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: as a gib cat or a lugged bear.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Or an old lion, or a lover's lute.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Yea, or the drone of a Lincolnshire bagpipe.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: What sayest thou to a hare, or the melancholy of
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Thou hast the most unsavoury similes and art indeed
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: the most comparative, rascalliest, sweet young
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: prince. But, Hal, I prithee, trouble me no more
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: with vanity. I would to God thou and I knew where a
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: commodity of good names were to be bought. An old
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: lord of the council rated me the other day in the
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: street about you, sir, but I marked him not; and yet
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: he talked very wisely, but I regarded him not; and
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: yet he talked wisely, and in the street too.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Thou didst well; for wisdom cries out in the
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: streets, and no man regards it.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: O, thou hast damnable iteration and art indeed able
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: to corrupt a saint. Thou hast done much harm upon
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: me, Hal; God forgive thee for it! Before I knew
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: thee, Hal, I knew nothing; and now am I, if a man
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: should speak truly, little better than one of the
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: wicked. I must give over this life, and I will give
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: it over: by the Lord, and I do not, I am a villain:
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: I'll be damned for never a king's son in
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Where shall we take a purse tomorrow, Jack?
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: 'Zounds, where thou wilt, lad; I'll make one; an I
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: do not, call me villain and baffle me.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: I see a good amendment of life in thee; from praying
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: to purse-taking.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Why, Hal, 'tis my vocation, Hal; 'tis no sin for a
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: man to labour in his vocation.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Poins! Now shall we know if Gadshill have set a
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: match. O, if men were to be saved by merit, what
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: hole in hell were hot enough for him? This is the
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: most omnipotent villain that ever cried 'Stand' to
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Good morrow, Ned.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Good morrow, sweet Hal. What says Monsieur Remorse?
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: what says Sir John Sack and Sugar? Jack! how
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: agrees the devil and thee about thy soul, that thou
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: soldest him on Good-Friday last for a cup of Madeira
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: and a cold capon's leg?
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: Sir John stands to his word, the devil shall have
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: his bargain; for he was never yet a breaker of
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: proverbs: he will give the devil his due.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Then art thou damned for keeping thy word with the devil.
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: Else he had been damned for cozening the devil.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: But, my lads, my lads, to-morrow morning, by four
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: o'clock, early at Gadshill! there are pilgrims going
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: to Canterbury with rich offerings, and traders
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: riding to London with fat purses: I have vizards
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: for you all; you have horses for yourselves:
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: Gadshill lies to-night in Rochester: I have bespoke
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: supper to-morrow night in Eastcheap: we may do it
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: as secure as sleep. If you will go, I will stuff
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: your purses full of crowns; if you will not, tarry
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: at home and be hanged.
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: Hear ye, Yedward; if I tarry at home and go not,
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: I'll hang you for going.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: You will, chops?
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: Hal, wilt thou make one?
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Who, I rob? I a thief? not I, by my faith.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: There's neither honesty, manhood, nor good
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: fellowship in thee, nor thou camest not of the blood
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: royal, if thou darest not stand for ten shillings.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Well then, once in my days I'll be a madcap.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Why, that's well said.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Well, come what will, I'll tarry at home.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: By the Lord, I'll be a traitor then, when thou art king.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Sir John, I prithee, leave the prince and me alone:
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: I will lay him down such reasons for this adventure
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: that he shall go.
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: Well, God give thee the spirit of persuasion and him
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: the ears of profiting, that what thou speakest may
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: move and what he hears may be believed, that the
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: true prince may, for recreation sake, prove a false
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: thief; for the poor abuses of the time want
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: countenance. Farewell: you shall find me in Eastcheap.
playData.speaker: FALSTAFF

playData.text_entry: Farewell, thou latter spring! farewell, All-hallown summer!
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Now, my good sweet honey lord, ride with us
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: to-morrow: I have a jest to execute that I cannot
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: manage alone. Falstaff, Bardolph, Peto and Gadshill
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: shall rob those men that we have already waylaid:
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: yourself and I will not be there; and when they
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: have the booty, if you and I do not rob them, cut
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: this head off from my shoulders.
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: How shall we part with them in setting forth?
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Why, we will set forth before or after them, and
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: appoint them a place of meeting, wherein it is at
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: our pleasure to fail, and then will they adventure
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: upon the exploit themselves; which they shall have
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: no sooner achieved, but we'll set upon them.
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: Yea, but 'tis like that they will know us by our
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: horses, by our habits and by every other
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: appointment, to be ourselves.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Tut! our horses they shall not see: I'll tie them
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: in the wood; our vizards we will change after we
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: leave them: and, sirrah, I have cases of buckram
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: for the nonce, to immask our noted outward garments.
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: Yea, but I doubt they will be too hard for us.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Well, for two of them, I know them to be as
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: true-bred cowards as ever turned back; and for the
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: third, if he fight longer than he sees reason, I'll
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: forswear arms. The virtue of this jest will be, the
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: incomprehensible lies that this same fat rogue will
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: tell us when we meet at supper: how thirty, at
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: least, he fought with; what wards, what blows, what
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: extremities he endured; and in the reproof of this
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: lies the jest.
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: Well, I'll go with thee: provide us all things
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: necessary and meet me to-morrow night in Eastcheap;
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: there I'll sup. Farewell.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Farewell, my lord.
playData.speaker: POINS

playData.text_entry: I know you all, and will awhile uphold
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: The unyoked humour of your idleness:
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Yet herein will I imitate the sun,
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Who doth permit the base contagious clouds
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: To smother up his beauty from the world,
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: That, when he please again to be himself,
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Being wanted, he may be more wonder'd at,
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: By breaking through the foul and ugly mists
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Of vapours that did seem to strangle him.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: If all the year were playing holidays,
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: To sport would be as tedious as to work;
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: But when they seldom come, they wish'd for come,
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: And nothing pleaseth but rare accidents.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: So, when this loose behavior I throw off
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: And pay the debt I never promised,
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: By how much better than my word I am,
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: By so much shall I falsify men's hopes;
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: And like bright metal on a sullen ground,
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: My reformation, glittering o'er my fault,
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Shall show more goodly and attract more eyes
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Than that which hath no foil to set it off.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: I'll so offend, to make offence a skill;
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Redeeming time when men think least I will.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: SCENE III. London. The palace.
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: Enter the KING, NORTHUMBERLAND, WORCESTER, HOTSPUR, SIR WALTER BLUNT, with others
playData.speaker: PRINCE HENRY

playData.text_entry: My blood hath been too cold and temperate,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Unapt to stir at these indignities,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: And you have found me; for accordingly
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: You tread upon my patience: but be sure
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: I will from henceforth rather be myself,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Mighty and to be fear'd, than my condition;
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Which hath been smooth as oil, soft as young down,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: And therefore lost that title of respect
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Which the proud soul ne'er pays but to the proud.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Our house, my sovereign liege, little deserves
playData.speaker: EARL OF WORCESTER

playData.text_entry: The scourge of greatness to be used on it;
playData.speaker: EARL OF WORCESTER

playData.text_entry: And that same greatness too which our own hands
playData.speaker: EARL OF WORCESTER

playData.text_entry: Have holp to make so portly.
playData.speaker: EARL OF WORCESTER

playData.text_entry: Worcester, get thee gone; for I do see
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Danger and disobedience in thine eye:
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: O, sir, your presence is too bold and peremptory,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: And majesty might never yet endure
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: The moody frontier of a servant brow.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: You have good leave to leave us: when we need
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Your use and counsel, we shall send for you.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: You were about to speak.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: To North
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Yea, my good lord.
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: Those prisoners in your highness' name demanded,
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: Which Harry Percy here at Holmedon took,
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: Were, as he says, not with such strength denied
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: As is deliver'd to your majesty:
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: Either envy, therefore, or misprison
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: Is guilty of this fault and not my son.
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: My liege, I did deny no prisoners.
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: But I remember, when the fight was done,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: When I was dry with rage and extreme toil,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Breathless and faint, leaning upon my sword,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Came there a certain lord, neat, and trimly dress'd,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Fresh as a bridegroom; and his chin new reap'd
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Show'd like a stubble-land at harvest-home;
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: He was perfumed like a milliner;
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And 'twixt his finger and his thumb he held
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: A pouncet-box, which ever and anon
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: He gave his nose and took't away again;
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Who therewith angry, when it next came there,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Took it in snuff; and still he smiled and talk'd,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And as the soldiers bore dead bodies by,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: He call'd them untaught knaves, unmannerly,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: To bring a slovenly unhandsome corse
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Betwixt the wind and his nobility.
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: With many holiday and lady terms
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: He question'd me; amongst the rest, demanded
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: My prisoners in your majesty's behalf.
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: I then, all smarting with my wounds being cold,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: To be so pester'd with a popinjay,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Out of my grief and my impatience,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Answer'd neglectingly I know not what,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: He should or he should not; for he made me mad
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: To see him shine so brisk and smell so sweet
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And talk so like a waiting-gentlewoman
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Of guns and drums and wounds,--God save the mark!--
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And telling me the sovereign'st thing on earth
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Was parmaceti for an inward bruise;
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And that it was great pity, so it was,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: This villanous salt-petre should be digg'd
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Out of the bowels of the harmless earth,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Which many a good tall fellow had destroy'd
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: So cowardly; and but for these vile guns,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: He would himself have been a soldier.
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: This bald unjointed chat of his, my lord,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: I answer'd indirectly, as I said;
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And I beseech you, let not his report
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Come current for an accusation
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Betwixt my love and your high majesty.
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: The circumstance consider'd, good my lord,
playData.speaker: SIR WALTER BLUNT

playData.text_entry: Whate'er Lord Harry Percy then had said
playData.speaker: SIR WALTER BLUNT

playData.text_entry: To such a person and in such a place,
playData.speaker: SIR WALTER BLUNT

playData.text_entry: At such a time, with all the rest retold,
playData.speaker: SIR WALTER BLUNT

playData.text_entry: May reasonably die and never rise
playData.speaker: SIR WALTER BLUNT

playData.text_entry: To do him wrong or any way impeach
playData.speaker: SIR WALTER BLUNT

playData.text_entry: What then he said, so he unsay it now.
playData.speaker: SIR WALTER BLUNT

playData.text_entry: Why, yet he doth deny his prisoners,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: But with proviso and exception,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: That we at our own charge shall ransom straight
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: His brother-in-law, the foolish Mortimer;
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Who, on my soul, hath wilfully betray'd
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: The lives of those that he did lead to fight
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Against that great magician, damn'd Glendower,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Whose daughter, as we hear, the Earl of March
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Hath lately married. Shall our coffers, then,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Be emptied to redeem a traitor home?
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Shall we but treason? and indent with fears,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: When they have lost and forfeited themselves?
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: No, on the barren mountains let him starve;
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: For I shall never hold that man my friend
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Whose tongue shall ask me for one penny cost
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: To ransom home revolted Mortimer.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Revolted Mortimer!
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: He never did fall off, my sovereign liege,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: But by the chance of war; to prove that true
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Needs no more but one tongue for all those wounds,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Those mouthed wounds, which valiantly he took
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: When on the gentle Severn's sedgy bank,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: In single opposition, hand to hand,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: He did confound the best part of an hour
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: In changing hardiment with great Glendower:
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Three times they breathed and three times did
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Upon agreement, of swift Severn's flood;
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Who then, affrighted with their bloody looks,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Ran fearfully among the trembling reeds,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And hid his crisp head in the hollow bank,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Bloodstained with these valiant combatants.
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Never did base and rotten policy
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Colour her working with such deadly wounds;
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Nor could the noble Mortimer
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Receive so many, and all willingly:
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Then let not him be slander'd with revolt.
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Thou dost belie him, Percy, thou dost belie him;
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: He never did encounter with Glendower:
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: He durst as well have met the devil alone
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: As Owen Glendower for an enemy.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Art thou not ashamed? But, sirrah, henceforth
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Let me not hear you speak of Mortimer:
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Send me your prisoners with the speediest means,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Or you shall hear in such a kind from me
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: As will displease you. My Lord Northumberland,
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: We licence your departure with your son.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Send us your prisoners, or you will hear of it.
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: Exeunt King Henry, Blunt, and train
playData.speaker: KING HENRY IV

playData.text_entry: An if the devil come and roar for them,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: I will not send them: I will after straight
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And tell him so; for I will ease my heart,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Albeit I make a hazard of my head.
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: What, drunk with choler? stay and pause awhile:
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: Here comes your uncle.
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: Re-enter WORCESTER
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: Speak of Mortimer!
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: 'Zounds, I will speak of him; and let my soul
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Want mercy, if I do not join with him:
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Yea, on his part I'll empty all these veins,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And shed my dear blood drop by drop in the dust,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: But I will lift the down-trod Mortimer
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: As high in the air as this unthankful king,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: As this ingrate and canker'd Bolingbroke.
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Brother, the king hath made your nephew mad.
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: Who struck this heat up after I was gone?
playData.speaker: EARL OF WORCESTER

playData.text_entry: He will, forsooth, have all my prisoners;
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And when I urged the ransom once again
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Of my wife's brother, then his cheek look'd pale,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And on my face he turn'd an eye of death,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Trembling even at the name of Mortimer.
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: I cannot blame him: was not he proclaim'd
playData.speaker: EARL OF WORCESTER

playData.text_entry: By Richard that dead is the next of blood?
playData.speaker: EARL OF WORCESTER

playData.text_entry: He was; I heard the proclamation:
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: And then it was when the unhappy king,
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: --Whose wrongs in us God pardon!--did set forth
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: Upon his Irish expedition;
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: From whence he intercepted did return
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: To be deposed and shortly murdered.
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: And for whose death we in the world's wide mouth
playData.speaker: EARL OF WORCESTER

playData.text_entry: Live scandalized and foully spoken of.
playData.speaker: EARL OF WORCESTER

playData.text_entry: But soft, I pray you; did King Richard then
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Proclaim my brother Edmund Mortimer
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Heir to the crown?
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: He did; myself did hear it.
playData.speaker: NORTHUMBERLAND

playData.text_entry: Nay, then I cannot blame his cousin king,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: That wished him on the barren mountains starve.
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: But shall it be that you, that set the crown
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Upon the head of this forgetful man
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And for his sake wear the detested blot
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Of murderous subornation, shall it be,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: That you a world of curses undergo,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Being the agents, or base second means,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: The cords, the ladder, or the hangman rather?
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: O, pardon me that I descend so low,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: To show the line and the predicament
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Wherein you range under this subtle king;
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Shall it for shame be spoken in these days,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Or fill up chronicles in time to come,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: That men of your nobility and power
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Did gage them both in an unjust behalf,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: As both of you--God pardon it!--have done,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: To put down Richard, that sweet lovely rose,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: An plant this thorn, this canker, Bolingbroke?
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: And shall it in more shame be further spoken,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: That you are fool'd, discarded and shook off
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: By him for whom these shames ye underwent?
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: No; yet time serves wherein you may redeem
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Your banish'd honours and restore yourselves
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR

playData.text_entry: Into the good thoughts of the world again,
playData.speaker: HOTSPUR
